OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny rain
OL,6,Fwill become increasingly isolated
OL,7,Fthrough the evening before clearing
OL,8,Feast around midnight. Largely dry with
OL,9,Fvariable amounts of cloud however, a
OL,10,Ffew isolated showers may push north
OL,11,Flater, most likely around dawn.
OL,12,FRemaining rather warm and humid.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FAny remaining showers will
OL,15,Fsoon clear east, leaving a dry but
OL,16,Fvery warm day with plenty of hazy
OL,17,Fsunshine. Light winds will do little
OL,18,Fto alleviate the heat.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
